Package Model

Class Property

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Space
      • Model.Property
  • public class Property
extends Space
    This extends the Space class to implement several methods and properties that indicate the behaviors of a Property.

      • Property

        public Property​(double[] rent,
                double[] price,
                double multiplier,
                java.lang.String color,
                int players,
                java.lang.String name)
        Creates a Property object through the specified parameters indicating a list of rent rates, price rates, multiplier, color, and name.
        Parameters:
        rent - array of values containing rates that differ depending on the level of development
        price - array of values containing the rates for development
        multiplier - unique multiplier of the Property
        color - String parameter indicating the color
        players - number of participating players in the game
        name - indicates the name of the Property
